# VSS collision model parameters for helium
#
# Variable Soft Sphere (VSS) parameters from:
#   G. A. Bird, "Molecular Gas Dynamics and the Direct Simulation of
#   Gas Flows", Oxford University Press, 1994, Appendix A (Tref = 273.15 K).
# For a VHS run, use diameter 2.33e-10 with alpha = 1.0 instead.

# diameter (m)
# omega
# tref
# alpha

He   2.30e-10  0.66  273.15  1.26
